	<Placemark id="5C3BDEEDBB000002">
		<name>Anhinga Trail</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div><span style="color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif"><span class="size" style="font-size:14px">The Anhinga Trail is a short trail in the Everglades National Park. Located 4 miles from the park entrance, it starts at the Royal Palm Visitor Center.</span></span></span><br></div>]]></description>
